# Copy to .env.local and fill in real values. .env.local is gitignored.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are inlined into the client bundle at BUILD time,
# so they must be present when `next build` / `docker build` runs — not
# just at container start. Pass them as build args if you use any.
#
# Server-only vars (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix) are read at runtime and can
# be supplied via env_file / -e when the container starts.

# Example server-only setting:
# APP_LOG_LEVEL=info
